		}
		{
			dependencies: ["58E9697AC16F146C"]
			description: ["&eDecomposition is complete, yielding a dark, crumbly medium teeming with active biology. This is the end goal, rich soil that can support agriculture and function as a self‑sustaining living system, promoting plat growth.&r"]
